snippet.title: Rhythm Sprout - Release Window Announcement + NEW DEMO
snippet.description:
PLAY THE NEW DEMO NOW

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1475840/Rhythm_Sprout_Sick_Beats__Bad_Sweets/
Featuring new levels, game modes and demo-exclusive story.

Full game launching early 2023 on PC, Switch, Xbox and PlayStation.

Rhythm Sprout is a fast-paced rhythm action with original music and a wacky story mode.
- Step to the rhythm / Fight to the beat
- Remix levels with modifiers
- Follow a quirky self-aware story in between

Join our Discord community to share your highscores
https://discord.gg/b94YvPZyVC
